n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家機器的運行，保證了統治階級對被統治階級的統治，從而保證了統治階級的利益。</span></span>當被統治階級對統治階級的不滿達到一定程度而發生反抗時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">統治階級所掌握的國家機器就會對反抗者進行鎮壓。</span></span>"},{"pid":"a91d53552f35b0b6fc2c9d1a2ac9dd6ad081ff04","tid":1320264,"uid":4043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca40cb1ebfdb8c37c2b18969edc054ff2a1d715","tid":1320264,"uid":194894,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"洗佢老味白，唔洗旨意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。當時咁大力打示威者，依家見勢色唔對就話慘？我屌你老母啊，打示威者個陣有無諗過示威者慘啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"越洗越爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8819c8349bb287169fa5af6efc2a6a8c5dc829c","tid":1320264,"uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"你唔行動出黎倒戈, 唔會有人信你架<br />\n死黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd9624b8515e76b1975202566c73e41af6864c4","tid":1320264,"uid":41507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你真係咁撚感性你點解唔做d野改變下"},{"pid":"4a7a404a1a0d4d735e5d3cb458b07570eeb2437a","tid":1320264,"uid":4043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8819c8349bb287169fa5af6efc2a6a8c5dc829c","tid":1320264,"uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"你唔行動出黎倒戈, 唔會有人信你架<br />\n死黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"所言甚是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd2dadd494c74e2429fa28d459b8b7540600d50",